Suzanne Bing https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Suzanne_Bing 0 Suzanne Bing (10 March 1885 – 22 November 1967) was a French actress. She was a founding member of Jacques Copeau's Théâtre du Vieux-Colombier in Paris during the first season 1913-14. Later she worked with the troupe in New York from 1917-19 and again in Paris, 1920-24. Suzanne_Bing ( 10_March_1885 – 22_November_1967 ) was a_French_actress .
